OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear skies
OL,6,Fthrough much of the evening, before
OL,7,Fpatches of low cloud and fog move
OL,8,Fslowly northwards across the region
OL,9,Fovernight. Remaining dry and
OL,10,Frelatively mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FMorning fog and low cloud
OL,13,Fwill lift to give a dry and mild day,
OL,14,Fwith brighter spells. Cloud will
OL,15,Fthicken from the west in the
OL,16,Fafternoon, with possible rain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
